# Authentication Rules (NextAuth / Auth.js)

- Use official Prisma adapter.
- Do not invent auth tables manually.
- Protect write endpoints server-side.

## Environment Variables

Required:

- DATABASE_URL
- NEXTAUTH_SECRET (or AUTH_SECRET depending on version)
- Provider credentials (if using OAuth)

Never commit secrets.
Update .env.example when adding new variables.
